reviewText: Vinod Khanna in a black turtleneck, Pran and Iftekhar as members of a gang of thieves, and one of the greatest nightclub numbers EVER (though sadly not featuring Helen). Woooo!
Gaddaar film was released in 1973 by director and producer Harmesh Malhotra. Main cast in this film are Vinod Khanna, Yogita Bali,And Ranjeet.
